biography: Rasmus, a celebrated name from Vihti Golf Club, is known for his captivating presence on the golf course.

While Rasmus only participated in the Hector Trophée once, his mark on the tournament is palpable. Known for his strategic mind and calm demeanor, Rasmus approaches each game with a calculated precision that keeps spectators on the edge of their seats.
Although Rasmus is considered retired from the Hector Trophée, his fans will always remember his contributions to the competition.
